        "Speaker": "卡罗琳",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc14ep4_npc002_14",
        "zh_CN": "陶董，我觉得我应该是管不了了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 116,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 4,
        "Speaker": "卡罗琳",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc14ep4_npc002_15",
        "zh_CN": "没有了分析员在这里主持场面，好像整个家里一下子就乱了套。",
