        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 9,
        "Speaker": "陶",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc14ep4_npc003_02",
        "zh_CN": "辰星已经做出了决定，你确定还要按照原定计划进行吗？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 122,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "忽然，陶毫无征兆地问了这么一句话。而紧接着在她的眼中，像是有一行文字浮现。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 123,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 9,
        "Speaker": "陶",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc14ep4_npc003_03",
        "zh_CN": "放心不下吗，也是，她们都是你的珍宝。而且……出于各种考量，你也必须抵达现场。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 124,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 9,
        "Speaker": "陶",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc14ep4_npc003_05",
        "zh_CN": "我知道了，后方我会看好的。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 125,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 4,
        "Speaker": "卡罗琳",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc14ep4_npc002_16",
        "zh_CN": "刚才那是……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 126,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 5,
        "Speaker": "陶",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc14ep4_npc003_06",
        "zh_CN": "就是你想的那样。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 127,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 4,
        "Speaker": "卡罗琳",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc14ep4_npc002_17",
        "zh_CN": "分析员啊。真该让他自己好好来看看这幅场面，这么大的事，谁都冷静不下来。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 128,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 5,
        "Speaker": "陶",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc14ep4_npc003_07",
        "zh_CN": "也包括你吗？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 129,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 4,
        "Speaker": "卡罗琳",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc14ep4_npc002_18",
        "zh_CN": "……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 130,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 5,
        "Speaker": "陶",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc14ep4_npc003_08",
        "zh_CN": "卡罗琳说这样的话，是心有不甘吧。",
