        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 4,
        "Speaker": "卡罗琳",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc14ep4_npc002_20",
        "zh_CN": "格拉尼“灵蹄”已经准备运输了。肴和分析员都完成了转移。",
        "disable": 0
